and my parents barely
ever let me leave our house.

81
00:04:03,176 --> 00:04:05,616
Well, when a small bump could
stop your heart, it makes sense.

82
00:04:06,046 --> 00:04:08,174
But you still have
a lot of friends?

83
00:04:08,448 --> 00:04:11,247
Yeah, of course. I mean, I just
can't do anything fun with them.

84
