Well, in case you haven't
noticed, I like to talk.

87
00:04:20,761 --> 00:04:21,888
- And, uh...
- Yes.

88
00:04:22,095 --> 00:04:23,655
We all do everything
online now anyway.

89
00:04:24,865 --> 00:04:26,743
The first thing I'm gonna
do when I get out of here

90
00:04:26,767 --> 00:04:28,531
