friends to a concert.

91
00:04:28,602 --> 00:04:30,628
Like, general
admission, on the floor.

92
00:04:30,704 --> 00:04:33,504
I don't even care who the band is,
just as long as the place is packed.

93
00:04:33,540 --> 00:04:35,099
Oh, and I'm gonna hug everyone.

94
00:04:35,308 --> 00:04:37,641
You've never hugged
anyone? Not even your parents?

95
00:04:37,978 --> 00:04:40,641
Kissed by my parents,
high-fived by my friends,

96
00:04:40,714 --> 00:04:42,808
but, nope, no hugs.

97
00:04:42,883 --> 00:04:44,442
It's just too risky.

98
00:04:45,752 --> 00:04:48,586
Hugs make me feel trapped.

99
00:04:50,991 --> 00:04:52,960
Sorry. Almost done.

100
00:04:53,493 --> 00:04:54,893
Pain in the upper
right quadrant.

101
00:04:55,228 --> 00:04:56,252
It's jaundice.

102
00:04:56,563 --> 00:04:57,895
Bilirubin's off the chart.

103
00:04:58,265 --> 00:04:59,699
That doesn't make sense.

104
00:04:59,766 --> 00:05:01,526
He's been doing so
well since the transplant.

105
00:05:01,601 --> 00:05:03,045
Every check-up this
year's been perfect.

106
00:05:03,069 --> 00:05:04,935
Well, it could just be
a temporary flare-up.

107
00:05:05,138 --> 00:05:07,903
We'll increase his anti-rejection
meds and do a full liver exam.

108
00:05:07,974 --> 00:05:08,998
We'll know more then.

109
00:05:17,951 --> 00:05:20,477
You two, do the work-up,
and you find a new liver.

110
00:05:20,821 --> 00:05:22,165
Shouldn't we wait
for the biopsy result?

111
00:05:22,189 --> 00:05:23,953
Not when I already
know what it's gonna say.

112
00:05:24,124 --> 00:05:25,683
He needs a new liver ASAP.

113
00:05:26,693 --> 00:05:29,253
I mean, that's gonna be
hard. He's blood type O.

114
00:05:29,329 --> 00:05:30,388
It's gonna be impossible.

115
00:05:30,463 --> 00:05:32,008
He's lucky they were
able to find the first one.

116
00:05:32,032 --> 00:05:33,409
Well, he better get lucky again

117
00:05:33,433 --> 00:05:35,129
'cause it's our only
way to keep him alive.

118
00:05:37,938 --> 00:05:38,962
We're screwed.

119
00:05:39,039 --> 00:05:42,271
Barbara Boxer got ear
barotrauma scuba diving in Cozumel

120
00:05:42,342 --> 00:05:44,538
and cannot fly for two weeks,
which means we don't have

121
